en $\\gamma$-ray and fast neutrons signals was not achieved and\nthe neutron capture feature was observed to overlap both the $\\gamma$-ray and\nfast neutron bands. Taking into account the electron light nonproportionality,\nthe neutron-capture light yield in EJ-254 was determined to be 89.4$\\pm$1.1\nkeVee.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Jan 2021 02:48:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-08"}
