iminary evidence that these\nhighly non-linear models and humans may use similar high-level factors for\nmaterial recognition tasks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Jan 2021 11:29:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 Feb 2021 12:35:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-05"}
