the alphabet and extremal conformal probabilities for this class of renewal\ntype shifts. We prove the existence and uniqueness of the eigenmeasure\nprobability of the Ruelle's transformation at low enough temperature for a\nparticular potential on the generalized renewal shift; such measures are not\ndetected on the standard renewal shift since for low temperatures, $\\beta F$ is\ntransient.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Jan 2021 14:13:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-08"}
